Module mk.musiclibrarygui

Package mk.musiclibrarygui.models

package mk.musiclibrarygui.models
This package contains the model classes for the music library GUI application. It includes classes for managing songs, handling song lists, and a custom exception.
Version:
2.0
Author:
Michal Kaminski
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    mk.musiclibrarygui
    The mk.musiclibrarygui package contains the main class required to run the Music Library GUI application.
    mk.musiclibrarygui.controllers
    Provides the controller classes for the music library application, handling user interactions and managing the application's UI flow.
  • Class
    Description
    Song
    The Song class represents a musical track with information about its ID, title, composer, album, release date, and duration.
    SongList
    The SongList class manages a collection of Song objects, providing methods to add, delete, and retrieve songs.
    WrongInputException
    The WrongInputException class is a custom exception that indicates an invalid input has been provided.
